7085 11.9995L13.2385 4.56152Z" fill="#976B43"></path></svg></a></div><div class="home-travel"><div class="container"><div class="home-travel__text"><h2 class="travel-title">一趟旅程，看見馬祖的<span>深度</span>與<span>靈魂</span></h2><p>一場深入島嶼記憶的旅程，從戰地遺跡、宗教廟宇、濱海風情與在地日常，帶你慢慢走進馬祖的文化、故事與生活節奏。</p></div></div><img src="/_next/static/media/fish.0a5c8f71.png" class="home-travel__fish" alt="decorate fish"/><img src="/_next/static/media/boat.ef71c8b4.png" class="home-travel__boat" alt="decorate boat"/></div><div class="home-recommend text-center py-5"><p>Loading...</p></div><section class="home-food relative py-12"><div class="container mx-auto px-4"><h2 class="title text-2xl font-bold mb-8">必吃美食</h2><div class="home-food__content"><div class="swiper arrow-fill"><div class="swiper-wrapper"></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div></div></div><img src="/_next/static/media/house-1.32830a50.png" class="home-food__house home-food__house-1" alt="decorate house icon 1"/><img src="/_next/static/media/house-2.48678146.png" class="home-food__house home-food__house-2" alt="decorate house icon 2"/><img src="/_next/static/media/house-3.d18c69ef.png" class="home-food__house home-food__house-3" alt="decorate house icon 3"/></div></section><div class="home-findus"><h2 class="title">你也可以在這裡找到我們</h2><div class="home-findus__link"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" title="馬祖愛趴GO粉絲團（另開新視窗）" aria-label="馬祖愛趴GO粉絲團（另開新視窗）" class="c-home-findus-link-item group flex items-center gap-3 transition-colors hover:text-primary" href="https://zh-tw.facebook.com/Go.go.Matsu"><span class="c-home-findus-link-item__icon text-xl"><svg width="48" height="49" viewBox="0 0 48 49" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M47.9002 23.6498V9.8498C47.9002 4.4498 43.5094 0.0498047 38.0208 0.0498047H23.9501H9.87942C4.39085 0.0498047 0 4.4498 0 9.9498V23.7498C0 23.9498 0 24.2498 0 24.4498V38.2498C0 43.6498 4.39085 48.0498 9.87942 48.0498H38.1206C43.5094 48.0498 48 43.6498 48 38.1498V24.3498C47.9002 24.1498 4